      "description": "This vehicle is being listed honestly as a car in poor condition \u2014 buyers should come in with realistic expectations. The exterior shows significant wear, including multiple areas of paint fading, scratches, and visible body damage. The interior has seen heavy use, with worn upholstery, damaged trim pieces, and general deterioration throughout the cabin. Mechanically, the car has known issues that will require attention and repair before it can be considered fully reliable. This listing is suited for a buyer who is mechanically inclined, looking for a project vehicle, or needs basic transportation and is prepared to invest in repairs. No attempt has been made to conceal the car's shortcomings \u2014 what you see is what you get, and we encourage a thorough pre-purchase inspection.",
